                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="upgradesFlexRow">
                    <div class="upbackground">
                        <div>
                            <img src="/images/upgrades/bumper_sticker.jpg" alt="Bumper Sticker">
                        </div>
                        <a>Bumper Stickers</a>
                    </div>
                        
                    <div class="upbackground">
                        <div>
                            <img src="/images/upgrades/hub-cap.jpg" alt="Hub Cap">
                        </div>
                        <a>Hub Caps</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reviews">
            <h2>DMC Delorean Reviews</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>"So fast it is almost like traveling in time." (4/5)</li>
                <li>"Coolest ride on the road." (4/5)</li>
